Description: The 'DiAna' (Disproportionality Analysis) package offers
    advanced tools for analyzing FDA Adverse Event Reporting System
    (FAERS) data, enhancing drug safety research. It enables users to
    download cleaned FAERS data and import relational datasets,
    facilitating case identification and control selection to minimize
    confounding in analyses. The package includes functions for
    descriptive and disproportionality analysis, time-to-onset analysis,
    network analysis, retrieval algorithms, and visualization.
